.TH "calipso_opt_update" 9 "calipso_opt_update" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
calipso_opt_update \- Replaces socket's hop options with a new set
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" calipso_opt_update
.BI "(struct sock *sk "  ","
.BI "struct ipv6_opt_hdr *hop "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sk" 12
the socket
.IP "hop" 12
new hop options
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Replaces \fIsk\fP's hop options with \fIhop\fP.  \fIhop\fP may be NULL to leave
the socket with no hop options.
